## Custom Styles

### When to Use Custom CSS

Only use custom CSS files for:
1. Complex animations that Tailwind can't handle
2. Component-specific styles that are reused
3. Third-party library overrides

### Custom CSS Pattern

```css
/* question-highlight.css */
.highlight-container {
  position: relative;
}

.highlight-text {
  background: linear-gradient(
    120deg,
    rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.3) 0%,
    rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.3) 100%
  );
  background-size: 100% 0.4em;
  background-position: 0 88%;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
}
```

Import in component:
```typescript
import './highlight.css'
```

